## ğŸ’¡ Intuition
A subarray `nums[l..r]` satisfies:

- Sum = `prefix[r] - prefix[l-1]`
- Length divisible by k â†’ `(r + 1) % k == l % k`

So we track **minimum prefix sum for each modulo class**.

